data.value: The MSI G274F 27" 180Hz IPS FHD Gaming Monitor is a powerhouse that will improve your gaming experience. With a Full HD resolution of 1920 x 1080, the IPS display provides bright colors and broad viewing angles, resulting in an immersive visual experience. The excellent 180Hz refresh rate and 1ms GtG reaction time accommodate fast-paced gaming scenarios, resulting in smooth and responsive gameplay. With two HDMI ports and one DisplayPort, you may connect a variety of devices. The display is G-Sync compliant, with adaptive sync technology that eliminates screen tearing and stuttering, resulting in a smooth and tear-free gaming experience.
